* Iron Raptor simply looked towards Scattershot as he tilted his head, 
movement from a distance drawing her attention towards the approaching Demon 
Wulf.*
<Oh, great!>
* She thought as she leaned her weight on one leg and tilted her own head, 
turning her eyes back towards Scatter.*

" You all may kill Kluster but you'll never get Prowl."

* She said calmly as she stood her ground.*

" How powers are probably even greater then mine! And you saw how mine are."

* She barely had time to get the sentence out before Scattershot was gone, 
towards the CF.
She was getting sick of this war, very sick of it.
But Iron Raptor braced herself as she tuned her eyes towards Demon Wulf as 
he approached, riasing her sword which was goving off a faint glow.
She may be sick of this fight but she wasn't a quiter, and she would fight 
until the last atom of her spark was deleted.
Iron Raptor waited for Demon Wulf, ready for more.*
